headline: These Were the 5 Top-Performing Stocks in the Dow Jones Industrial Average in 2024
summary: Rising over 13% in 2024, the Dow Jones Industrial Average lagged the S&P 500, which soared 23%.  While Boeing dragged the index down last year, Nvidia (NASDAQ: NVDA) took up the slack and was the best-performing Dow Jones stock of 2024.  Let's take a look at the other names that rounded out the top-performing Dow Jones stocks.
